{"tid":2317254,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"陳雲：我一早叫香港人唔好反送中","createTime":"2020-12-08T11:59:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T12:35:57.000Z","uid":78768,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ab693519c1226148e9d5f4ab11048eecd4e87f","tid":2317254,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:59:04.000Z","msg":"//陳雲：華麗轉身，出賣選民。泛民去年幫有錢佬叫窮人、窮青年上街反送中，保護有錢人在香港逃稅逃資。之後，泛民總辭。現在有錢佬籌組紫荊黨，取代泛民。<br />\n這些政治白手套的本領，高呀！<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">可憐的是被泛民送去反送中的窮青年。我一早叫香港人不要參加的，叫有錢佬自己去反，但香港人不領情，沒法。</span></span><br />\n（按：我引用2003年反二十三條的時候是有富豪上街陪伴一般市民的，故此當年差役好客氣。可惜2019年，青年人聽信泛民自己上街，沒有富豪做護駕，結果被差役痛打。這是政治常識，但香港人偏偏不聽我勸告，太遲啦。）//<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AgPLrHh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgPLrHh.png&h=f3c4e8d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be60bf324b384e1daca956bae3ff229391c59475","tid":2317254,"uid":78768,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:59:55.000Z","msg":"老師又中"},{"pid":"3e69c4b55618110a17eaea960a6250c49d403223","tid":2317254,"uid":226067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T11:59:56.000Z","msg":"請問反唔反有咩分別？"},{"pid":"0f5b2454d09d869d78a0ba126947770d152d8ca4","tid":2317254,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:00:25.000Z","msg":"陳雲風火輪"},{"pid":"1327bb717e5fba8d55f5eb3cd3e31abeb6858900","tid":2317254,"uid":78768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:07:35.000Z","msg":"唔係叫反送中，要叫「香港憲法保衛戰」"},{"pid":"b859fef398cb1f4a264749c2cfec26637e417a88","tid":2317254,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca9cef7189da6abccb73528dfa45f9b577196ab7","tid":2317254,"uid":283494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:35:57.000Z","msg":"點呀，陳雲替身"}]}